    <body.head>
      <hedline>
        <hl1>How's That Again?</hl1>
      </hedline>
      <abstract>
        <p>Chip Mergott letter about Apr 1 article on film Zoo says there is no lyrical side to bestiality (S)</p>
      </abstract>
    </body.head>
    <body.content>
      <block class="lead_paragraph">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
        <p>Re ''A Lyrical Approach to a Subject That Shocks'' [April 1]:</p>
        <p>It's finally occurred to me that Dennis Lim's article on the film ''Zoo'' isn't a satirical parody. This will probably brand me as a hopeless square but here goes: There isn't any ''lyrical'' side to the subject of bestiality.</p>
        <p>Chip Mergott  Doylestown, Pa.</p>
      </block>
      <block class="full_text">
        <p>To the Editor:</p>
